data.meta_description: Auto Race Car Driver. 11-time veteran of the Indianapolis 500 with 3 finishes in the Top Ten, finish a personal best 4th in 1952. He was also the 1950 Midwest sprint car racing champion and might be best remembered for his exploits on automobile racing's Black Sunday, July 29, 1951. On this day, three big-time drivers,...
